        <abstract>
            <p>Believes WDF’s case of mongrel Scotch deerhound is very valuable for him.</p>
            <p>Mentions his work on pigeons and chickens.</p>
            <p>Fears sometimes he will break down: "My subject gets bigger and bigger".</p>
        </abstract>
